# Keep the build context small and reproducible: never copy host-built artifacts
# or VCS metadata. The db-lib submodule is NOT copied from the context — the deps
# stage git-clones it at a pinned commit (see Dockerfile), which is the only thing
# that works on Railway (it doesn't init submodules or copy .git into the build
# context). Excluding it here shrinks the context and makes a local `docker build`
# reproduce Railway's empty-submodule condition.
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
.git
**/.git
supagloo-database-lib
*.log
npm-debug.log*
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
coverage
.vscode
.idea
